data.description: The current owners of this home want you to love it as much as they have.  Come grow your family in a home that feels like forever.  All 3 bedrooms have fresh paint and new wood trim, one bathroom has been completely redone with a shower ready for you to sing in, while the other bathroom has had a new, modern life breathed into it.  The rest of the home wants you to come see its new paint, trim work, new outlets, new garage door opener, all done in 2023, and new porch, steps and patio in 2022.  The very deep back yard is mostly fenced in and has a nice sized shed to keep your gardening tools.  All appliances stay, including washer and dryer and the furnace and A/C just went through their annual maintenance check in August and are ready to keep you comfortable.  This property is in a quiet neighborhood and backs up to an open field giving you a sense that you have just gotten away from it all.
